<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta id="viewport" name="viewport" content="width=device-width, height=device-height, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no,target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
    <title></title>
    <link href="~/css/Vpay.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <img src="~/img/vpay.jpg" />
    </header>
    <section>
        <p>订单提交成功，请你尽快付款！</p>
        <p>请您在提交订单后<span style="color: #DF8C4A;">5分钟</span>内完成支付，否则订单会自动取消</p>
        <p>订单号：<span>@ViewBag.orderno</span></p>
        @*<p>回调地址：<span>@ViewBag.callBackUrl</span></p>*@
        <p>应付金额：<span style="color: #3CC53C;">@ViewBag.amount</span></p>

        @*<p style="width:80%;margin-top:30px;background:#3CC53C;text-align:center;padding:15px 0;border-radius:5px"></p>*@
        <a href="@ViewBag.mweb_url" style="display: block;width: 80%;height: 50px;text-align: center;line-height: 50px;background-color: #3CC53C;margin-top: 52px;margin-left: 6%;border-radius:5px;color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold">点击支付</a>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
